<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-3"><a href="Russia#Early_history"><span class="tocnumber">2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Early history</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-4"><a href="Russia#Kievan_Rus&#39;"><span class="tocnumber">2.2</span> <span class="toctext">Kievan Rus'</span></a></li>
